data.title: Petition to rename street Russian Ambassy in The Hague to Aleksej Navalny road

images.description:
There is a petition going here in the Netherlands to rename the street in The Hague were the Russian Embassy is located to Aleksej Navalnyweg (Aleksej Navalny road).

This would have big consequences for the russian Embasy, all incoming mail, stationary, business cards and more would have Navalnys name on it.

Unfortunately its unlikely this is going to happen, The Hague has a strict policy for renaming existing streets. But i really like the idea.

This would be the ultimate troll directed to Putin

Link to dutch news site
https://nos.nl/artikel/2509837-roep-om-aleksej-navalnyweg-bij-russische-ambassade-in-den-haag

data.title: Been replaying this conversation for hours

images.description:
Edit: Uh, wow, I did not think this would take off. Thanks, all!

And to respond generally to some comments: no I didn't think this was a good way to flirt or that he would actually pick up on anything based on me commenting on the moon. I panicked when I saw an opening for some chat away from the rest of the group and couldn't think of a normal conversation topic, so when I saw the moon and remembered thinking it looked so pretty earlier that night, my brain just grabbed on to it and ran.
